riel Box, for The Seventh Veil (1945), which received the 1946 Oscar for best original screenplay.Sydney and Muriel married in 1935, had a daughter Leonora the following year, and divorced in 1969. Source: Wikidata; 01/08/2023", "biography_author": null, "date_of_biography": "2025-03-12T00:35:21.901316+11:00", "external_links": [{"id": 5236, "uri": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sydney_Box"}], "uuid": "96f0ea65-62b1-4418-87e1-c6dd201dc728", "source": {"name": "Vernon", "slug": "vernon"}, "source_identifier": "29413", "external_references": [{"id": 26839, "source": {"name": "Wikidata", "slug": "wikidata"}, "source_identifier": "Q2373669"}, {"id": 31715, "source": {"name": "VIAF", "slug": "viaf"}, "source_identifier": "59281476"}, {"id": 31716, "source": {"name": "LOC Auth", "slug": "loc-auth"}, "source_identifier": "n94040658"}, {"id": 31717, "source": {"name": "WorldCat", "slug": "worldcat"}, "source_identifier": "lccn-n94040658"}], "date_modified": "2025-03-12T00:35:21.901628+11:00"}]}